OL,5, A man was killed in a hit-and-run crash
OL,6, shortly after police left him barefoot 
OL,7, outside an Iceland store three miles   
OL,8, from home, a court has heard.          
OL,10,FGareth Roper was struck in Wigan by a  
OL,11,FVolvo driven by Jamie Evans, 30, and   
OL,12,Fdied later with severe head injuries.  
OL,14,FEvans, who did not have a licence,     
OL,15,Fadmitted causing the death of Mr Roper,
OL,16,F35, by dangerous driving at Bolton     
OL,17,FCrown Court earlier this year.         
OL,19,FHe was remanded in custody and is due  
OL,20,Fto be sentenced on Tuesday.            
